h3. Problem Definition
Currently, organizations are counting the number of requests based in the reporter, which means that if the reporter is part of more than one organization, the request will be counted on each organization, when it's actually just one request.

h3. Suggested Solution
Change the filter retrieving the issues so instead of the reporter of the issue it'll be looking at the organization field:
h6. Current
{code}
reporter in organizationMembers(Pricing)
{code}

h3. Workaround 
None.

